<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī sakasaṁvatsarada 1168 neya parābhavasaṁ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vatsarada Āśvaja svu 11 sō śrīviśvarū
<lb n="3" break="no"/>padēvargge baḷḷeyaraṟeya sāteyanāya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kena tāyi nāgauve hūvina paḍige ko
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭṭa gadyāṇa voṁdaṟa baḍḍige <unclear>di</unclear>naṁprati 50
<lb n="6"/>puḻpavanu Āca<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>drārkkatāraṁbaraṁ pūjārigaḷu naḍasuvaru <g type="ddanda">.</g>
